<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَتَجُوزُ الحَوَالَةُ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> عَلَى دَيْنٍ مُسْتَقِرٍّ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> إِنِ اتَّفَقَ الدَّيْنَانِ جِنْساً، وَوَقْتاً، وَوَصْفاً، وَقَدْراً.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- وَتَصِحُّ بِخَمْسَةٍ عَلَى خَمْسَةٍ مِنْ عَشَرَةٍ، وَعَكْسُهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيُعْتَبَرُ رِضَا:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- مُحِيلٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَمُحْتَالٍ عَلَى غَيْرِ مَلِيءٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَالصُّلْحُ فِي الأَمْوَالِ قِسْمَانِ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">أَحَدُهُمَا:</span> عَلَى الإِقْرَارِ،<span class="c5"> وَهُوَ نَوْعَانِ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> الصُّلْحُ عَلَى جِنْسِ الحَقِّ، مِثْلُ أَنْ يُقِرَّ لَهُ بِدَيْنٍ أَوْ عَيْنٍ،<span class="c5"> فَيَضَعَ أَوْ يَهَبَ لَهُ البَعْضَ وَيَأْخُذَ البَاقِيَ:</span> فَيَصِحُّ:<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> مِمَّنْ يَصِحُّ تَبَرُّعُهُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> بِغَيْرِ لَفْظِ صُلْحٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> بِلَا شَرْطٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>